cn.trinea.android.common.service.impl

类 SimpleCache<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.trinea.android.common.service.impl.SimpleCache<K,V>
  • 所有已实现的接口:

    直接已知子类:
    PreloadDataCache

    public class SimpleCache<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Cache<K,V>, java.io.Serializable
    Simple Cache
      Usage
    • Use one of constructors below to construct cache
    • setCacheFullRemoveType(CacheFullRemoveType) set remove type when cache is full
    • setValidTime(long) set valid time of elements in cache, in mills
    • put(Object, CacheObject) or put(Object, Object) put element
    • get(Object) get element
    • loadCache(String) restore cache from file
    • saveCache(String, SimpleCache) save cache to file
      Constructor
    • SimpleCache()
    • SimpleCache(int)
    • loadCache(String) restore cache from file
      About hit and miss of the cache
    • getHitRate() get hit rate of the cache
    • getHitCount() get hit count of the cache
    • getMissCount() get miss count of the cache
      About size of cache
    • getMaxSize() get the maximum capacity of the cache
    • getSize() get the number of elements in the cache valid
      Other interfaces same to Map
    作者:
    Trinea 2011-12-23
    另请参阅:

      • SimpleCache

        public SimpleCache()
        • Maximum size of the cache is DEFAULT_MAX_SIZE
        • Elements of the cache will not invalid, can set by setValidTime(long)
        • Remove type is RemoveTypeEnterTimeFirst when cache is full

      • SimpleCache

        public SimpleCache(int maxSize)
        • Elements of the cache will not invalid, can set by setValidTime(long)
        • Remove type is RemoveTypeEnterTimeFirst when cache is full
        参数:
        maxSize - maximum size of the cache
